title: Hummus Bistro D&A
typeOfFood: Lacto, Ovo, Mediterranean, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. About half the menu is vegetarian, of which some are vegan or can be made vegan. Staff is knowledgeable about the menu. No hard alcohol. Dogs are welcome.  Reservations possible but not required. Free Wi-Fi. Child-friendly.
